===LED燈泡===
很多LED燈均可取代螺旋式熱熾燈或省電燈泡，由5-40瓦特，低功率的熱熾燈，至60瓦特（只需約7瓦特電力）。截至2010年，有些燈甚至能取代更高功率的燈泡，例如一顆13瓦特的燈泡就與100瓦特熱熾燈的光度相約。{{Citation needed|date=July 2010}}（一般的熱熾燈光效標準，約為14至17流明/瓦特，視乎其大小和電壓而定。根據歐盟標準，一顆與60瓦特熱熾燈等效的「節能燈泡」，最少要能輸出806流明。）<ref name="Lonsdale">Sarah Lonsdale, "[http://www.telegraph.co.uk/property/greenproperty/7873021/Green-property-energy-efficient-bulbs.html Green property: energy-efficient bulbs] {{Wayback|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/property/greenproperty/7873021/Green-property-energy-efficient-bulbs.html |date=20100710051946 }}," ''Telegraph,'' July 7, 2010</ref>)

多數的LED燈泡都是設計成不可調暗的，但亦有些能配合調光器操作，而且光照角度較窄。由2010年起，這些燈泡開始由30至50美元的價錢下跌。LED燈泡比[[省電燈泡|省電燈泡]]更省電<ref>Elisabeth Rosenthal and Felicity Barringer, "[http://www.nytimes.com/2009/05/30/science/earth/30degrees.html?ref=lightemitting_diodes Green Promise Seen in Switch to LED Lighting] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2009/05/30/science/earth/30degrees.html?ref=lightemitting_diodes |date=20110702184631 }}," ''New York Times'', May 29, 2009</ref>，若散熱合宜，壽命長達30000小時。熱熾燈一般都只有1000小時壽命，省電燈泡亦只有大約8000小時。<ref name="LED misrepresentations">Justin Maeers, [http://www.modbs.co.uk/news/fullstory.php/aid/7779/LED_misrepresentations.html LED misrepresentations] {{Wayback|url=http://www.modbs.co.uk/news/fullstory.php/aid/7779/LED_misrepresentations.html |date=20201030074532 }}, May 2010</ref>故LED燈泡能使用大約25至30年，而且光度的隨年月衰減很少。[[能源之星|能源之星]]標準訂明燈泡使用6000小時後，光度衰減應在10%之內，最差不可超過15%。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Integral LED Lamps Criteria Development|url=http://www.energystar.gov/ia/partners/manuf_res/downloads/IntegralLampsFINAL.pdf|accessdate=2011-01-29|archive-date=2020-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200928155527/https://www.energystar.gov/ia/partners/manuf_res/downloads/IntegralLampsFINAL.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>不像螢光燈，LED燈泡都是無汞的。LED燈泡亦有不同顏色選擇。售價雖然較高，但電力和維護費用較低，可互相抵消。<ref name="BBB">{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2009/09/25/technology/25bulb.html|title=Build a Better Bulb for a $10 Million Prize|date=2009-09-24|first=Eric|last=Taub|coauthor=leora Broydo Vestel|accessdate=2010-02-06|publisher=New York Times|archive-date=2020-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130052104/https://www.nytimes.com/2009/09/25/technology/25bulb.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

